## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="acb3a-102">設計工具搜尋物件的即時屬性值，並以程式碼會產生這些值的引擎透過序列化本身的程式碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="acb3a-102">Designers serialize themselves to code through an engine that searches through the live property values of objects and generates those values as code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="acb3a-103">因此，比方說，按鈕的文字會以下列格式產生。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="acb3a-103">So, for example, the text of a button is generated in the following format.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
this.okButton.Text = "OK";  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="acb3a-104">其中一個限制，其中此配置是很難擷取的屬性，從另一個位置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="acb3a-104">One of the limitations of this scheme is that it is difficult to retrieve a property from another location.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="acb3a-105">例如，它很難發出格式如下的程式碼，因為唯一的程式碼產生器可以依賴屬性中的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="acb3a-105">For example, it is very difficult to emit code in the following format, because the only thing the code generator can rely on is the value in the property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
this.titleLabel.Text = this.Text;  
```  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="acb3a-106"><xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService>簡化擷取屬性值從另一個位置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="acb3a-106">The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService> simplifies retrieval of a property value from another location.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="acb3a-107">設計工具可以存取此服務，以指定另一個的值指派給該一個成員。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="acb3a-107">A designer can access this service to dictate that one member is assigned the value of another.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="acb3a-108">程式碼產生器時產生程式碼，這類關聯性搜尋，如果兩個成員之間的關聯性找到程式碼產生器，它會發出程式碼關聯性，而不是搜尋的屬性值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="acb3a-108">The code generator searches for such relationships when generating code, and if a relationship between two members is found the code generator, it emits code for the relationship rather than searching for the property value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="acb3a-109">使用先前的文字指派做為範例，下列程式碼範例顯示設計階段用來建立關聯性的程式碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="acb3a-109">Using the previous text assignment as an example, the following code example shows design time code used to establish a relationship.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
object titleLabel, form;  
PropertyDescriptor titleLabelText = TypeDescriptor.GetProperties(titleLabel)["Text"];  
PropertyDescriptor formText = TypeDescriptor.GetProperties(form)["Text"];  
MemberRelationshipService ms = GetService(typeof(MemberRelationshipService);  
ms[titleLabel, titleLabelText] = new MemberRelationship(form, formText);  
```
